name: FSourceEffectMotionFilterSettings
doc:
FSourceEffectMotionFilterSettings
This is the source effect's setting struct.

MotionFilterTopology: In Serial Mode, Filter A will process then Filter B will process; in Parallel mode, Filter A and Filter B will process the dry input seprately, then be mixed together afterward.
MotionFilterMix: Filter Mix controls the amount of each filter in the signal where -1.0f outputs Only Filter A, 0.0f is an equal balance between Filter A and B, and 1.0f outputs only Filter B. How this blend works depends on the Topology.
